{{Lunisolar September}} '''September 16''' is the 16th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Emperor Sujin|ja|崇神天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 12nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|86 BC|ja|紀元前86|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}） – The imperial court conducted its first nationwide population and household registration. * {{ill|Shōryaku|ja|正暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|991|ja|991|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Emperor Ichijō|ja|一条天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} conferred the title of {{ill|Nyoin-gō|ja|女院号|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} upon the empress dowager, {{ill|Saneko Fujiwara|ja|藤原詮子|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, marking the first instance of a 【female院号】. * {{ill|Ōtoku|ja|応徳|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1086|ja|1086|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Fujiwara Michitoshi|ja|藤原通俊|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} compiled the anthology {{ill|Goshūi Wakashū|ja|後拾遺和歌集|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
