{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=九月十六|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 9월 16일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar September|qq=}} '''September 16''' is the 16th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Emperor Sujin|ja|崇神天皇|qq=draft|qq=}} 12nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|86 BC|ja|紀元前86|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|qq=draft|qq=}}） – The imperial court conducted its first nationwide population and household registration. * {{ill|Shōryaku|ja|正暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|991|ja|991|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Emperor Ichijō|ja|一条天皇|qq=draft|qq=}} conferred the title of {{ill|Nyoin-gō|ja|女院号|qq=draft|qq=}} upon the empress dowager, {{ill|Saneko Fujiwara|ja|藤原詮子|qq=draft|qq=}}, marking the first instance of a 【female院号】. * {{ill|Ōtoku|ja|応徳|qq=draft|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1086|ja|1086|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Fujiwara Michitoshi|ja|藤原通俊|qq=draft|qq=}} compiled the anthology {{ill|Goshūi Wakashū|ja|後拾遺和歌集|qq=draft|qq=}}.
== Births == * {{ill|An'ei|ja|安永|qq=draft|qq=}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1779|ja|1779|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 25|ja|10月25日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Ichikawa Beian|ja|市河米庵|qq=draft|qq=}}, a calligrapher ({{ill|Calligrapher|ja|書家|qq=draft|qq=}}) (died {{ill|1858|ja|1858|qq=draft|qq=}}). * {{ill|Kansei|ja|寛政|qq=draft|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1793|ja|1793|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 20|ja|10月20日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Watanabe Kasan|ja|渡辺崋山|qq=draft|qq=}}, a rangaku scholar and painter (died {{ill|1841|ja|1841|qq=draft|qq=}}). * {{ill|Bunka|ja|文政|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1804|ja|1804|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 19|ja|10月19日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Hosokawa Saigo|ja|細川斉護|qq=draft|qq=}}, the head of the {{ill|Kumamoto Domain|ja|熊本藩|qq=draft|qq=}} (died {{ill|1860|ja|1860|qq=draft|qq=}}). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1855|ja|1855|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Komura Jutaro|ja|小村壽太郎|qq=draft|qq=}}, Minister of Foreign Affairs (died {{ill|1911|ja|1911|qq=draft|qq=}}).
