{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=九月十六|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 9월 16일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar September|qq=}} '''September 16''' is the 16th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/September (Lunisolar)|qq=}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shakkō|qq=}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Emperor Sujin|ja|崇神天皇|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Sujin|qq=}} 12nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|86 BC|ja|紀元前86|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/86 BC|qq=}} {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 12|qq=}}） – The imperial court conducted its first nationwide population and household registration. * {{ill|Shōryaku|ja|正暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōryaku|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|991|ja|991|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/991|qq=}} {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 26|qq=}}) – {{ill|Emperor Ichijō|ja|一条天皇|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Ichijō|qq=}} conferred the title of {{ill|Nyoin-gō|ja|女院号|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nyoin-gō|qq=}} upon the empress dowager, {{ill|Saneko Fujiwara|ja|藤原詮子|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Saneko Fujiwara|qq=}}, marking the first instance of a 【female院号】. * {{ill|Ōtoku|ja|応徳|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtoku|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1086|ja|1086|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1086|qq=}} {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 26|qq=}}) – {{ill|Fujiwara Michitoshi|ja|藤原通俊|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fujiwara Michitoshi|qq=}} compiled the anthology {{ill|Goshūi Wakashū|ja|後拾遺和歌集|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Goshūi Wakashū|qq=}}.
== Births == * {{ill|An'ei|ja|安永|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/An'ei|qq=}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1779|ja|1779|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1779|qq=}} {{ill|October 25|ja|10月25日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 25|qq=}}) – {{ill|Ichikawa Beian|ja|市河米庵|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ichikawa Beian|qq=}}, a calligrapher ({{ill|Calligrapher|ja|書家|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Calligrapher|qq=}}) (died {{ill|1858|ja|1858|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1858|qq=}}). * {{ill|Kansei|ja|寛政|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kansei|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1793|ja|1793|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1793|qq=}} {{ill|October 20|ja|10月20日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 20|qq=}}) – {{ill|Watanabe Kasan|ja|渡辺崋山|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Watanabe Kasan|qq=}}, a rangaku scholar and painter (died {{ill|1841|ja|1841|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1841|qq=}}). * {{ill|Bunka|ja|文政|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunka|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1804|ja|1804|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1804|qq=}} {{ill|October 19|ja|10月19日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 19|qq=}}) – {{ill|Hosokawa Saigo|ja|細川斉護|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hosokawa Saigo|qq=}}, the head of the {{ill|Kumamoto Domain|ja|熊本藩|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kumamoto Domain|qq=}} (died {{ill|1860|ja|1860|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1860|qq=}}). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1855|ja|1855|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1855|qq=}} {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 26|qq=}}) – {{ill|Komura Jutaro|ja|小村壽太郎|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Komura Jutaro|qq=}}, Minister of Foreign Affairs (died {{ill|1911|ja|1911|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1911|qq=}}).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Tennen|ja|天永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tennen|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1111|ja|1111|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1111|qq=}} {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 7|qq=}}) – {{ill|Ōe Masafusa|ja|大江匡房|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōe Masafusa|qq=}}, a kugyō, Confucian scholar, and poet (born {{ill|1041|ja|1041|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1041|qq=}}). * {{ill|Genkyū|ja|元久|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genkyū|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1204|ja|1204|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1204|qq=}} {{ill|November 27|ja|11月27日|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 27|qq=}}) – {{ill|Hojo Masanori|ja|北条政範|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hojo Masanori|qq=}}, a military commander (武将) (born {{ill|1189|ja|1189|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1189|qq=}}). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=|12=simpl