== Births == * {{ill|An'ei|ja|安永|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/An'ei|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 安永 (元号)}} 8th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1779|ja|1779|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1779|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:October 25|October 25]]) – {{ill|Ichikawa Beian|ja|市河米庵|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ichikawa Beian|qq=}}, a calligrapher ({{ill|Calligrapher|ja|書家|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Calligrapher|qq=|comment=enwiki is a redirect}}) (died {{ill|1858|ja|1858|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1858|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}). * [[:en:Kansei|Kansei]] 5th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1793|ja|1793|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1793|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:October 20|October 20]]) – [[:en:Watanabe Kazan|Watanabe Kasan]], a rangaku scholar and painter (died {{ill|1841|ja|1841|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1841|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}). * [[:en:Bunsei|Bunka]] 1st year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1804|ja|1804|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1804|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1000}} [[:en:October 19|October 19]]) – {{ill|Hosokawa Saigo|ja|細川斉護|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hosokawa Saigo|qq=}}, the head of the [[:en:Kumamoto Domain|Kumamoto Domain]] (died {{ill|1860|ja|1860|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1860|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}). * [[:en:Ansei|Ansei]] 2nd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1855|ja|1855|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1855|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:October 26|October 26]]) – [[:en:Komura Jutarō|Komura Jutaro]], Minister of Foreign Affairs (died {{ill|1911|ja|1911|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1911|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1911 (曖昧さ回避)}}).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Ten'ei|Tennen]] 2nd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|1111|ja|1111|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1111|qq=|comment=enwiki is a redirect}} [[:en:December 7|December 7]]) – [[:en:Ōe no Masafusa|Ōe Masafusa]], a kugyō, Confucian scholar, and poet (born [[:en:1041|1041]]). * [[:en:Genkyū|Genkyū]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|1204|ja|1204|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1204|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1000}} [[:en:November 27|November 27]]) – {{ill|Hojo Masanori|ja|北条政範|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hojo Masanori|qq=}}, a military commander (武将) (born {{ill|1189|ja|1189|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1189|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}). * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 10th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1839|ja|1839|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1839|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:December 10|December 10]]) – {{ill|Matsudaira Saiatsu|ja|松平斉厚|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Matsudaira Saiatsu|qq=}}, a daimyō (born {{ill|1783|ja|1783|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1783|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}). * [[:en:Ansei|Ansei]] 3rd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1856|ja|1856|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1856|qq=}} [[:en:December 2|December 2]]) – {{ill|Ashidai Hirokun|ja|足代弘訓|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashidai Hirokun|qq=}}, a kokugakuist ({{ill|Kokugakuist|1=Kokugakusha|2=ja|3=国学者|ja|国学者|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kokugakuist|13=User:Immanuelle/Kokugakusha|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 国学}}) (born {{ill|1785|ja|1785|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1785|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}). * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 2nd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1869|ja|1869|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1869|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1000}} [[:en:December 7|December 7]]) – [[:en:Ōmura Masujirō|Ōmura Masujirō]], a military scholar (born {{ill|1824|ja|1824|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1824|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1000}}).
