== Deaths == * [[:en:Ten'ei|Tennen]] 2nd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1111|1111]] [[:en:December 7|December 7]]) – [[:en:Ōe no Masafusa|Ōe Masafusa]], a kugyō, Confucian scholar, and poet (born [[:en:1041|1041]]). * [[:en:Genkyū|Genkyū]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1204|1204]] [[:en:November 27|November 27]]) – {{ill|Hojo Masanori|ja|北条政範|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hojo Masanori|qq=}}, a military commander (武将) (born [[:en:1189|1189]]). * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 10th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1839|ja|1839|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1839|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:December 10|December 10]]) – {{ill|Matsudaira Saiatsu|ja|松平斉厚|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Matsudaira Saiatsu|qq=}}, a daimyō (born [[:en:1783|1783]]). * [[:en:Ansei|Ansei]] 3rd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1856|ja|1856|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1856|qq=}} [[:en:December 2|December 2]]) – {{ill|Ashidai Hirokun|ja|足代弘訓|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashidai Hirokun|qq=}}, a kokugakuist ({{ill|Kokugakuist|1=Kokugakusha|2=ja|3=国学者|ja|国学者|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kokugakuist|13=User:Immanuelle/Kokugakusha|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 国学}}) (born [[:en:1785|1785]]). * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 2nd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1869|ja|1869|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1869|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1000}} [[:en:December 7|December 7]]) – [[:en:Ōmura Masujirō|Ōmura Masujirō]], a military scholar (born [[:en:1824|1824]]).
